import DarkModeIcon from '@mui/icons-material/DarkMode'; // Add this import
import LightModeIcon from '@mui/icons-material/LightMode'; // Add this import

const Navbar = () => {
  const colorMode = useContext(ColorModeContext);
  const currentIcon = colorMode.mode === 'dark' ? <LightModeIcon /> : <DarkModeIcon />; // Determine which icon to show

  return (
    <AppBar position="static">
      <Toolbar>
        <Typography variant="h6" style={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
          A-IQ
        </Typography>
        <Button color="inherit" component={Link} to="/">
          Home
        </Button>
        <Button color="inherit" component={Link} to="/about">
          About Us
        </Button>
        <Button color="inherit" component={Link} to="/contact">
          Contact Us
        </Button>
        <Button color="inherit" component={Link} to="/login">
          Login
        </Button>
        <Button color="inherit" component={Link} to="/signup">
          Sign Up
        </Button>
        <IconButton color="inherit" onClick={colorMode.toggleColorMode}>
          {currentIcon} {/* Add the icon here */}
        </IconButton>
      </Toolbar>
    </AppBar>
  );
};
